name: 1736 Family Crisis
review_text:
My Counselor Rose N was the most help and Supportive person Iâ€™ve ever known. She made me feel stronger! She encouraged me! Through talking with her I became Empowered as a single mom of 3 young children dealing with a current abuser.. I am stronger today because of the years of Seeing her. My children Love Rose! She helped us redirect our life for the positive. I no longer live in fear. My children are happy. I told her my story and Rose believed me , even when the police did not take me seriously, Rose & Susan L & Katherine S. always took me serious and actually witness first hand the trouble I was in. Being a victim of DV sucks!! It really hurts when the LA law enforcement belittles the situation.. These fine ladies never doubted me.
I thank all three of you for your Support to me and my children. Our lives are forever changed.

Your Holliday Generosity brought tears to my eyes every year!!! Thank you Thank You Thank You !!

The Other staff at 1736 are always so nice and helpful and generous. We are so humbled by your kindness.
